    • Method Detail

      • cleanRegister

        public void cleanRegister​(int lockCards)
        Removes all cards that should not be locked in the register. Will remove last card in the register until only the correct number of locked cards remain
        Parameters:
        lockCards - how many card to lock down.

      • add

        public void add​(IProgramCards.Card[] newCardsToRegister)
        Adds an ArrayList of Cards to the start of the register. If any cards are locked into position, the new cards will end up the next vacant positions.
        Parameters:
        newCardsToRegister - the cards to be added to the register
